graph TD
    REQ[LLM Call<br/>Request] --> DC{Daily Budget<br/>Remaining?}

    DC -->|No| DP[Pause Until<br/>Midnight]
    DC -->|Yes| WC{Weekly Budget<br/>Remaining?}

    WC -->|No| WP[Pause Until<br/>Monday]
    WC -->|Yes| GC{Goal Budget<br/>Remaining?}

    GC -->|No| GP[Pause Goal<br/>Re-queue 5min]
    GC -->|Yes| OC{Operation<br/>Under $25?}

    OC -->|No| RJ[Reject Call]
    OC -->|Yes| EX[Execute<br/>LLM Call]

    EX --> TR[Track Cost<br/>Update Counters]
    TR --> AL{Budget < 25%?}
    AL -->|Yes| NT[Discord Alert]
    AL -->|No| OK[Continue]

    style REQ fill:#4a9eff,color:#fff
    style EX fill:#2ecc71,color:#fff
    style DP fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff
    style GP fill:#ff9f43,color:#fff
